headline.print_headline: Thai Protesters Rally Against PM Ahead of Senate Vote
headline.main: Thai Protesters Rally Against PM Ahead of Senate Vote

lead_paragraph: Tens of thousands of Thai anti-government protesters rallied across Bangkok on Saturday in their latest bid to topple Prime Minister Yingluck Shinawatra, a day before a crucial vote to elect a new Senate.
